§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit 00_THESIS § AXIOMS
  t∞: ω-field = the-One-True-State (per §§ 30_SUBSTRATE_v2)
       ≡ ¬ ECS-archetype-pool ¬ scene-graph
  t∞: manifestation = field-evolution-event ¬ designer-spawn-call
       ≡ rising-edge .radiance > τ → solid-spawn ; deterministic-rule
  t∞: every-manifestation audit-attributed
       ≡ (origin-cap, intent-tag, ts_micros, cell-coord) per-spawn

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ Ω-FIELD-AS-TRUTH  «foundation»

  § FACET-RECAP  (from §§ 30_SUBSTRATE_v2 § FACET-SEMANTICS)
    M  Material-identity   : 1-bit-tag + 63-bit-id (PGA-handle | RegionID)
    S  State-dynamics      : density + velocity + vorticity + enthalpy + bivector
    P  Probe-radiance      : 16B SH-coeffs (radiance_probe_lo + _hi)
    Φ  Pattern-handle      : 4B index into PhiTable (HDC 10000-D semantic-id)
    Σ  Consent-low-cache   : 4B low-half of full SigmaMaskPacked

  § OVERLAYS  (sparse Morton-keyed, per §§ 30_v2 § OVERLAYS)
    Λ-overlay : symbol-lattice token-buckets (event-tagged cells)
    Ψ-overlay : Wigner-magic non-classicality scalars
    Σ-overlay : full 16B-mask for non-default consent

  § Σ-MASK-PER-CELL-RECAP
    consent_bits : Observe Modify Sample Translate Recrystallize
                   Destroy Spawn Mark + reserved
    sovereignty_handle : u16 ; NULL = unclaimed/public
    capacity_floor + reversibility_scope + audit_seq + agency_state

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ SEED-CELLS  «intent → ω-field-perturbation»

  § STRESS-OBJECT-KINDS  ‼ canonical-14-set  (stage-1)
    1.  rock-cluster        : dense + low-velocity + opaque
    2.  vapor-plume         : low-density + high-vorticity + emissive
    3.  crystal-shard       : structured-grid + optical-anisotropy
    4.  flame-tongue        : high-enthalpy + audio-emission
    5.  metal-strut         : high-density + Sovereign-claimed
    6.  liquid-droplet      : moderate-density + surface-tension
    7.  bone-fragment       : structured + low-conductivity
    8.  fungus-bloom        : low-density + slow-growth-vorticity
    9.  wire-mesh           : sparse + high-conductivity
    10. silk-thread         : low-mass + high-tensile (Λ-tag flexible)
    11. ash-cloud           : particle-puff + low-cohesion
    12. coral-branch        : structured-grid + slow-evolution
    13. shadow-pool          : low-radiance + Φ-tag occlusion-marker
    14. lattice-cage        : structured + Sovereign-protected (player-built)

  § SEED-STAMPING  «intent → cell-coord → field-mutation»
    1. router emits Intent::SpawnCondensation { kind, location, attribs }
    2. SubstrateMutateCap consulted ; cap-grant-or-deny
    3. cell-coord resolved : Morton-key from location-vec3
    4. cell-touched via OmegaField::set_cell (Σ-check NON-OPTIONAL)
       ≡ Spawn-bit required in consent_bits @ that-cell ; SIG0003 if-missing
    5. seed-cell facets initialized per stress-object-kind table
    6. audit-entry appended : (cap, intent-tag, ts, cell-coord)

  § SPONTANEOUS-PAD-ZONE
    location  : NE corner of ScaleRoom @ [25, 1.5, -32] world-coords
    extent    : 8m × 8m × 4m bounding-box
    pre-claim : Σ-mask-default pre-set to allow-Spawn within-zone
    rationale : sandbox-zone where seeds can-condense w/o full-Sovereign-dance
                ≡ player can-experiment ; substrate can-evolve

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ EVOLUTION  «Phase-2 PROPAGATE drives field forward»

  § Wave-Unity  (per §§ 30_v2 § WAVE-UNITY-INTEGRATION)
    band-config : 5-band (4 LIGHT + 1 AUDIO) stage-1 default
    timestep    : multi-rate per-band (1ms LIGHT + AUDIO ; 100ms HEAT defer)
    boundary    : SDF-Robin-BC + KAN-impedance Z(λ, embedding)
    cross-band  : LIGHT→AUDIO shimmer ; LIGHT→MANA = 0 STRICT

  § COHOMOLOGY  (Phase-4)
    persistent-homology over emerged-region
    region-genus tracked ; cycle-emergence detected → Λ-token-emit
    informs : "new-shape-formed" event for narrative

  § ENTROPY-BOOK  (Phase-6)
    9 conservation-rows checked per-tick
    audit-chain epoch advanced once-per-tick
    HEAT-band absorbs all-losses

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ MANIFESTATION  «field-state → renderable-spawned-solid»

  § RISING-EDGE-DETECTOR
    radiance_summary = mean(P-facet across-seeded-cells in spawn-zone)
    threshold        : τ = 0.45 (configurable per spawn-class)
    when radiance_summary crosses-up-through τ :
      1. lock spawn-zone Σ-mask : Modify→Active, Spawn→consumed
      2. extract field-state : (M-facet majority, S-facet aggregates, Φ-handle)
      3. compose-into stress-object instance : (kind, pose, attribs)
      4. register w/ Stage-3..Stage-9 pipeline as-renderable
      5. emit ManifestationEvent : (cap, intent-tag, ts, cell-coord, kind)

  § ATTRIBUTE-AUDIT  ‼ load-bearing
    every-manifestation carries provenance :
      origin_cap         : SubstrateMutateCap-token-id used
      intent_tag         : enum-tag from Intent variant
      ts_micros          : monotonic spawn-timestamp
      cell_coord_morton  : Morton-key of seed-anchor-cell
      sovereign_handle   : u16 if Sovereign-claimed
    ≡ every spawned-thing answers : "who summoned me, when, why"

  § REVERSIBILITY
    manifestation reversibility-scope per §§ 30_v2 § REVERSIBILITY-SCOPE
    Substep      : revoke-this-tick ; trial-spawn allowed
    Session      : revoke-on-session-end ; common
    Permanent    : Sovereign-required ; rare ; scenes saved

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ WHY-BETTER-THAN-PROCGEN  «paradigm-comparison»

  § PROCGEN  (P1 in §§ 01)
    rule-table + seed → output
    ✓ deterministic + cache-friendly + low-cost
    ✗ predetermined : output ⊑ rule-table-image
    ✗ ¬ open-vocabulary : adding rule = code-change
    ✗ ¬ Σ-mask-aware : consent-not-encoded-in-rule
    ✗ ¬ Sovereign-handle-respected
    ✗ ¬ replay-bit-equal-across-hosts unless rule-impl-bit-stable

  § SPONTANEOUS-CONDENSATION  (P4 → P7)
    seed-cells + ψ-PDE + Σ-mask + Φ-binding → emergent-trajectories
    ✓ emergent ¬ enumerated : output NOT bounded-by-table
    ✓ open-vocabulary : new-Φ-handle = new-meaning ; no-code-change
    ✓ Σ-mask-aware structural : every-cell-touch consent-checked
    ✓ Sovereign-handle-respected : claimed-cells require authorizing
    ✓ replay-bit-equal : ω-field-evolution deterministic (R-9 §§ 30_v2)
    ✓ multiplicative-composition with-other-novelty-paths

  § THE-TRADE
    spontaneous : higher-cost-per-cell ; sparse-Morton + multi-rate amortizes
    procgen     : near-zero-cost-per-call ; but bounded-expressivity
    LoA-decision: 11.1ms Quest-3-frame can-afford spontaneous within
                   spawn-zone ; non-spawn-zones use procgen-fallback

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ EMERGENCE-EXAMPLES  «illustrative ¬ exhaustive»

  § PLAYER-TYPES "make a wire-cage"
    intent      : SpawnCondensation { kind: WireMesh, loc: gaze-target, ... }
    seed-cells  : sparse-grid lattice-pattern stamped @ target-cell
    evolution   : ψ-PDE propagates conductivity-aware boundaries
    cohomology  : closed-cycle detected → "cage" identified
    manifest    : WireMesh stress-object spawned ; HUD shows attribution
    next-text   : player can "twist it" → re-perturb same-cells

  § PLAYER-TYPES "burn the bridge"
    intent      : SpawnCondensation { kind: FlameTongue, loc: bridge, ... }
    Σ-check     : bridge claimed by-Sovereign-X (NPC) ; Spawn-bit OFF
    SIG0003     : compile-time refusal (¬ runtime-attempt)
    fallback    : DialogDM "the bridge resists your fire"
    ≡ consent-discipline structurally-prevents griefing

